{"tid":1245092,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再話人搞分化，我地的確係亂","createTime":"2019-06-20T07:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T09:23:08.000Z","uid":260209,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6f10f18625d73ff9f8970a9fe9f546c371709e2c","tid":1245092,"uid":260209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T07:25:17.000Z","msg":"又開始多人討論衝唔衝，就算叫人唔好互屌搞分化都於事無補，始終大家意見唔同。<br />\n<br />\n我地既優勢係人多，但亦容易自亂陣腳<br />\n我地係咪應該要開始有系統地管理人手？例如分組？<br />\n前線、物資、Fact checking、網上造勢、捉鬼隊等等<br />\n另外溝通平台都要諗，telegram同連登都唔太安全<br />\n<br />\n我地要諗辦法等唔同意見而同一立場既唔好分化，有默契地爬山<br />\n<br />\n一齊brainstorm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b0781b5e5babc5fa126d92204b93ba5c90520b","tid":1245092,"uid":260209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:06:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14434d678770e05e84548bc86cea52d328b4a38c","tid":1245092,"uid":260209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:06:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c24b3bac3fc29b6a8daf62c41b0eb685e934e9e","tid":1245092,"uid":260209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:09:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3ef72f13e9bfe957f6eab5a6a6381e102bf46a0","tid":1245092,"uid":260209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:09:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c843739569bb4aee8c0d0067994b29b21d51ea2","tid":1245092,"uid":260209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:10:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a533c92ba21975308bc57b58f24c20b0ef5f7f78","tid":1245092,"uid":260209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:23:08.000Z","msg":"推"}]}